data.description: Sellers Motivated** Arthur Rutenberg custom POOL home on half acre lot in gated community! 4 bedrooms 3 full baths plus two half baths AND private study off the master, as well as den/flex space! Side entry 3 car garage, brick paver drive and entry. Some of the homes features include: wood flooring, crown molding & granite throughout the home, double sided see-through fireplace in master bedroom & bath as well as another fireplace in the family room, custom cabinetry in the updated kitchen, heated pool, outdoor kitchen w/cooktop, large covered lanai, iron fencing, coffered ceilings, tray ceilings, architectural columns, built-in's, 8 ft interior doors, ceiling fans, plantation shutters, NEW TILE ROOF 2022, Tesla solar panels and battery 2021, both AC units and hot water tank replaced since 2019, intercom system, alarm, custom shelving in large master walk-in closet, separate makeup vanity, garden tub in master, separate shower stall, dual sinks, large master bedroom overlooks pool & features built-in's around the fireplace. Zoned for Windermere High School!
